  "title": "Immersive Melodies",
  "description": "Play custom melodies on various instruments and annoy your friends!",
  "body": "<!--suppress HtmlDeprecatedAttribute -->\n<div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center\">\n<img width=\"872\"\nsrc=\"https://cdn.conczin.net/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,w=872,f=png,q=90/https://cdn.conczin.net/immersive-melodies/banner.png\"\nalt=\"Screenshot\"/>\n<p>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/immersive-melodies\">\n<img alt=\"Modrinth\"\nsrc=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Modrinth-NA?style=for-the-badge&logo=modrinth&logoColor=000000&color=00AF5C\">\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/immersive-melodies\">\n<img alt=\"CurseForge\"\nsrc=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/CurseForge-NA?style=for-the-badge&logo=curseforge&logoColor=000000&color=F16436\">\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/agxcvAdj2a\">\n<img alt=\"Discord\"\nsrc=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Discord-NA?style=for-the-badge&logo=discord&logoColor=000000&color=5865F2\">\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/Luke100000/ImmersiveMelodies\">\n<img alt=\"Github\"\nsrc=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Github-NA?style=for-the-badge&logo=github&color=181717\">\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://crowdin.com/project/immersive-collection\">\n<img alt=\"Translate via Crowdin\"\nsrc=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Crowdin-NA?style=for-the-badge&logo=crowdin&color=2E3340\">\n</a>\n</p>\n\n<p>\nWhether you want to create a band, annoy your friends or just want Skeletons playing Megalovania while storming\nyour base, this mod got it all.\n</p>\n\n<p>\nPlay 25 bundled songs on 7 instruments, or upload your own melodies via simple <b>drag and drop in-game</b> or\nusing datapacks.\nWorks on multiplayer! Supports MIDI and ABC files, with several million of such available across the internet.\nYes birbs dance.\n</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n<p><img src=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/mcr/atlas?minecraft_version=1.20.1&locations=_immersive_melodies%3Ainstruments&dependencies=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2FLuke100000%2FImmersiveMelodies%2Ftree%2F1.20.1&resolution=48&background=fancy&row_size=8\" alt=\"Generated Atlas Image\"/></p>\n\n<iframe allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/YW1wXcHp_nA?wmode=transparent\"\nheight=\"480\" width=\"872\"></iframe>\n\n<img width=\"872\"\nsrc=\"https://cdn.conczin.net/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,w=872,f=jpeg,q=90/https://cdn.conczin.net/immersive-melodies/screenshots/screen1.jpg\"\nalt=\"Screenshot\"/>\n<img width=\"872\"\nsrc=\"https://cdn.conczin.net/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,w=872,f=jpeg,q=90/https://cdn.conczin.net/immersive-melodies/screenshots/screen3.jpg\"\nalt=\"Screenshot\"/>\n<img width=\"872\"\nsrc=\"https://cdn.conczin.net/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,w=872,f=jpeg,q=90/https://cdn.conczin.net/immersive-melodies/screenshots/screen2.jpg\"\nalt=\"Screenshot\"/>\n\n<p>Awesome paper texture by <a href=\"https://legacy.curseforge.com/members/soytutta/projects\">soytutta</a>!</p>\n\n<p>All recipes are unlocked and visible in the vanilla recipebook after collecting a copper ingot.</p>\n\n\n\n\n<p><img src=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/mcr/recipes?minecraft_version=1.20.1&locations=immersive_melodies%3A.%2A&dependencies=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2FLuke100000%2FImmersiveMelodies%2Ftree%2F1.20.1&resolution=32&animated=False&row_width=835\" alt=\"Generated Recipes Image\"/></p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<h1>Immersive Collection</h1>\n<p>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/immersive-armors\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=Immersive%20Armors&description=A%20lot%20of%20unique%20and%20vanilla-faithful%20armor%20sets.&icon_url=https%3A//cdn.conczin.net/immersive-armors/icon.png&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"Immersive Armors\"/>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/immersive-aircraft\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=Immersive%20Aircraft&description=A%20bunch%20of%20rustic%20aircraft%20to%20travel%2C%20transport%2C%20and%20explore%21&icon_url=https%3A//cdn.conczin.net/immersive-aircraft/icon.png&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"Immersive Aircraft\"/>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/immersive-melodies\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=Immersive%20Melodies&description=Play%20custom%20melodies%20on%20various%20instruments%20and%20annoy%20your%20friends%21&icon_url=https%3A//cdn.conczin.net/immersive-melodies/icon.png&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"Immersive Melodies\"/>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/immersive-paintings\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=Immersive%20Paintings&description=Drag%20and%20drop%2C%20pixelate%20and%20hang%20up%20beautiful%20art.&icon_url=https%3A//cdn.conczin.net/immersive-paintings/icon.png&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"Immersive Paintings\"/>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/immersive-optimization\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=Immersive%20Optimization&description=A%20lightweight%20entity-tick-scheduler%20for%20doubling%20your%20TPS.&icon_url=https%3A//cdn.conczin.net/immersive-optimization/icon.png&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"Immersive Optimization\"/>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/selectivebounds\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=SelectiveBounds&description=Hides%20the%20ugly%20block%20selection%20outline%20when%20not%20relevant.&icon_url=https%3A//cdn.conczin.net/selectivebounds/icon.png&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"SelectiveBounds\"/>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/man-of-many-planes\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=Man%20of%20Many%20Planes&description=A%20set%20of%20additional%20aircraft%20for%20Immersive%20Aircraft%20with%20Create%20support%20in%20mind.&icon_url=https%3A//cdn.conczin.net/man-of-many-planes/icon.png&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"Man of Many Planes\"/>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/immersive-machinery\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=Immersive%20Machinery&description=A%20bunch%20of%20rustic%20machinery%20to%20transport%2C%20mine%2C%20and%20automate%20things.&icon_url=https%3A//cdn.conczin.net/immersive-machinery/icon.png&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"Immersive Machinery\"/>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/immersive-furniture\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=Immersive%20Furniture&description=Create%20custom%20and%20fancy%20furniture%20in-game%20or%20choose%20from%20a%20vast%20online%20library.&icon_url=https%3A//cdn.conczin.net/immersive-furniture/icon.png&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"Immersive Furniture\"/>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/immersive-gateways\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=Immersive%20Gateways&description=Mysterious%2C%20long-forgotten%20portals%20scattered%20across%20the%20Overworld.&icon_url=https%3A//cdn.conczin.net/immersive-gateways/icon.png&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"Immersive Gateways\"/>\n</a></p>\n\n<h1>Addons</h1>\n<p>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/arids-immersive-resprites\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=Arids%20Immersive%20Resprites&description=Resprites%20for%20the%20Immersive%20Melodies%20and%20Immersive%20Paintings%20mods%21&icon_url=https%3A//cdn.conczin.net/common/icons/arids-immersive-resprites.webp&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"Arids Immersive Resprites\"/>\n</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.conczin.net/common/pixel.png?immersive_pages_hash=078639759938ce7e2578220d68517599\" alt=\"The page hash for easier page deployment.\"/>",
